1
00:00:00,780 --> 00:00:04,780
Today we vote for a new leader of the Western Alliance.

2
00:00:04,780 --> 00:00:08,220
So let's vote.

3
00:00:08,220 --> 00:00:12,220
No one should have a problem with my re-election.

4
00:00:12,220 --> 00:00:15,220
My family are dominant in this city.

5
00:00:15,220 --> 00:00:18,059
I vote Pietro.

6
00:00:18,059 --> 00:00:19,059
What?

7
00:00:19,059 --> 00:00:23,059
Does anyone need reminding that I am still the boss?

8
00:00:23,059 --> 00:00:26,059
Everyone knows your son's been rung shared the last five years.

9
00:00:26,059 --> 00:00:28,059
I vote Pietro too.

10
00:00:28,059 --> 00:00:31,250
I abstain if too young.

11
00:00:31,250 --> 00:00:33,250
Although we could do with some fresh blood.

12
00:00:33,250 --> 00:00:36,250
Arm and a matter of while always be your son.

13
00:00:36,250 --> 00:00:43,270
My favorite heir.

14
00:00:43,270 --> 00:00:46,270
I will hand over the business to you in advance.

15
00:00:46,270 --> 00:00:49,270
Consider it a wedding gift.

16
00:00:49,270 --> 00:00:52,579
I'm worried.

17
00:00:52,579 --> 00:00:55,579
We'll get everything you wish for, Father.

18
00:00:55,579 --> 00:00:57,579
So this was all part of your plan.

19
00:00:57,579 --> 00:00:58,579
Plan?

20
00:00:58,579 --> 00:01:00,579
Wasn't the wedding an impromptu decision?

21
00:01:00,579 --> 00:01:04,719
Not very well that I'm in charge now.

22
00:01:04,719 --> 00:01:10,579
You need to remember that this is just the white wedding by law.

23
00:01:10,579 --> 00:01:15,099
The real ceremony for the mafia is the black wedding.

24
00:01:15,099 --> 00:01:21,189
And without my blessing, he will never be recognized by the family.

25
00:01:21,189 --> 00:01:23,189
This wedding's important to me.

26
00:01:23,189 --> 00:01:27,189
I inherited the family in advance to make sure no one took advantage of the situation.

27
00:01:27,189 --> 00:01:30,189
No matter what, I'm still your son.

28
00:01:30,189 --> 00:01:32,189
And I want your blessing.

